<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.7">
<l>kāppārā rivviṭattu kaṅkiruḷi ṉuṇṭuḷiyāy</l>
<l>cēṭpāla tūḻiyāyc celkiṉṟa kaṅkulvāy</l>
<l>tūppāla veṇcaṅku cakkarattaṉ ṟōṉṟāṉā</l>
<l>ṟīppāla valviṉaiyēṉ ṟeyvaṅkā ḷeṉceykēṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who will guard [me] in this place? During the night</l>
<l>that goes [on] as a faraway aeon, as fine drops of rimmed darkness,</l>
<l>the one with the discus [and] the pure white conch will not appear.</l>
<l>O gods, what will I do [who has done] deeds harsh as fire?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
